{"tid":59771,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[黑仔玩嘢] 回應俄羅斯黑客干預美總統選舉 奧巴馬下令驅逐35名俄外交官出境","createTime":"2016-12-30T02:17:59.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-30T05:41:51.000Z","uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"12a561c52e4501f1fe3f99eb0bfe81e967a90af7","tid":59771,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T02:17:59.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】俄羅斯涉嫌透過黑客干預美國總統選舉，美國總統奧巴馬下令驅逐35名俄羅斯外交官員。<br />\n<br />\n奧巴馬周四發聲明公布一系列制裁措施，回應美國指俄羅斯黑客干預美國總統選舉的行動，包括下令驅逐35名俄羅斯外交人員出境，限他們帶同家眷在72小時內離開。<br />\n<br />\n奧巴馬發表聲明指，這批外交人員涉嫌在美國境內從事與外交官員身分不符的活動，並且關閉兩幢分別位於紐約及馬里蘭州的俄羅斯建築物，相信他們在這些建築物進行收集情報的工作。<br />\n<br />\n奧巴馬表示，華府曾先後多次向莫斯科當局發出警告但無效，所以有必要採取措施回應，防止俄羅斯繼續損害美國利益及違反國際規範，他又警告制裁措施陸續有來。<br />\n<br />\n克里姆林宮批評制裁非法，質疑候任總統特朗普是否同意有關制裁，又表明會採取報復行動。"},{"pid":"d7d884df1de98b810dfef65bfdc990c5ed7e28ab","tid":59771,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T02:21:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f04a1deea1feab1e26d42517be33ecb6917e9031","tid":59771,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T02:23:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20161111/55903117\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20161111%2F55903117&d=e%2FsC%2FBdbtYRdGnAOuN7emZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=bdfc3437\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20161111%2F55903117&h=ea7a5b0d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20161111/55903117</a>"},{"pid":"5d141f484e6df0d245631a03214ed929ed630e19","tid":59771,"uid":1139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T02:24:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"